# ⚔️ Funny Battle Simulator

## Overview

Funny Battle Simulator is the largest permanent mini game introduced during the Roblox Buddy AI Anniversary Event.

Players create their own armies, unlock units, fuse characters, build custom strategies, and fight in hilarious physics-based battles.

This game is designed to become one of Roblox Buddy AI's signature games.

---

# 👥 Player Modes

Supports:

- 🤖 1 vs AI Buddy
- ⚔️ 1 vs 1
- 👥 2 vs 2
- 👥 3 vs 3
- 👥 5 vs 5
- 👥 10 vs 10

---

# 🎯 Objective

Defeat the opponent's army using strategy, unit combinations, teamwork and custom formations.

---

# 🪖 Army Creation

Players can build armies in four different ways.

## A. Budget Mode

Players receive a limited budget.

Each unit has a cost.

Players must create the strongest army possible within the budget.

---

## B. Map Discovery

Some units randomly spawn around maps.

Players can explore and permanently unlock them.

---

## C. Trading

Players can trade units with friends.

---

## D. Fusion Machine

Players can fuse any two units.

Examples:

🤖 Robot + 🐔 Chicken

👻 Ghost + 🎃 Pumpkin

🎅 Santa + 🦌 Reindeer

Unlimited combinations are possible.

---

# 🧬 Fusion System

Unlimited Fusion Combinations.

Every fusion combines:

- Health
- Damage
- Special Ability
- Appearance

No rarity restrictions.

---

# 📖 Secret Recipe Book

A hidden Recipe Book is located inside Buddy's House.

The Recipe Book contains:

- Known Recipes
- Locked Recipes
- Secret Recipes

Each recipe displays:

- Required Units
- Health
- Damage
- Special Powers

---

# 📚 Fusion Index

Separate from the Recipe Book.

Players can track:

- Discovered Fusions
- Locked Fusions
- Completion Progress

---

# 👤 Unit Classes

Every unit belongs to a class.

Examples:

⚔️ Melee

🏹 Archer

🔫 Gunner

🛡️ Tank

⚡ Mage

💉 Healer

💣 Bomber

🐎 Cavalry

🤖 Mechanical

👑 Boss

Players unlock units permanently.

---

# 🎮 Player Control

Players may choose:

- Watch the battle
- Control one unit directly
- Become Army Leader
- Fly above the battlefield and command the army

---

# 👑 Commander Mode

Players command their army by clicking locations.

Commands include:

- Move
- Attack
- Defend
- Follow
- Retreat

---

# 🤖 AI Battle

Players can test their army against Buddy AI.

Difficulty:

- Easy
- Normal
- Hard
- Expert
- Nightmare
- Impossible

---

