# 😂 Funny Physics

Every battle features exaggerated physics.

Examples:

- Flying Units
- Rolling Characters
- Explosions
- Slow Motion
- Knockback
- Funny Falls

---

# ⚡ Special Powers

Every unit has a unique special ability.

Fusion creates new combined abilities.

---

# 🌦️ Random Battle Events

Visual events may occur.

Examples:

- Rain
- Snow
- Thunder
- Darkness
- Volcano

Gameplay is NOT affected.

Players can disable visual events in Settings.

