- Fusion Materials
- Units
- Cosmetics
- Leaderboard Points

Luck influences bonus rewards.

---

# 🏆 Ranked Battles

Ranks include:

- Bronze
- Silver
- Gold
- Diamond
- Master
- Champion
- Legend

---

# 🎨 Custom Content

Players may create:

- Custom Maps
