---

# 🎥 Replay System

Every completed battle can be replayed.

Players can watch important moments again.

---

# 👀 Spectator Mode

Players may freely spectate battles.

They can switch between any surviving unit.

---

# Long-Term Vision

Funny Battle Simulator is designed to become one of Roblox Buddy AI's biggest permanent games with unlimited replayability through custom armies, fusion mechanics, funny physics, and community creativity.

